      "content": "i just cant make it to a clinic right now, work is crazy and doctors are so expensive here. i was thinking i could just try some antiseptic drops or maybe even just use some warm compresses and regular eye drops for a few days to see if it clears up? it doesnt feel THAT bad, just a bit annoying.",
